des:
DEENKEE products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off your devices.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your DEENKEE devices - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.

After connecting Alexa to your DEENKEE devices products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "DEENKEE" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register an account in our "DEENKEE" app;
(3). You need to have some DEENKEE devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "DEENKEE" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "DEENKEE HOME" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "DEENKEE HOME" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "DEENKEE HOME", and you'll be navigated to "DEENKEE" login page;
(9). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(10). Now all setup is finished.

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on 'robot name'.”
“Alexa, turn off 'robot name'.”
